This is the **BetterRest** app built as part of my **52-Apps-in-52-Weeks Challenge**.

## ðŸ“± App Overview
BetterRest helps users calculate their **ideal bedtime** based on:
- Desired wake-up time
- Amount of sleep
- Daily coffee intake

It uses **CoreML** with a trained **SleepCalculator.mlmodel** to predict when you should go to bed.

---

## ðŸš€ Features
- SwiftUI Interface (Form layout)
- DatePicker for wake-up time
- Stepper controls for Sleep Hours & Coffee Intake
- **CoreML Prediction** (SleepCalculator.mlmodel)
- Presents ideal bedtime via Alert
- Fully responsive on iPhone 16 Pro (Simulator)

